### Screenshots / Working Demo

Here are some screenshots showing the working of the AI-Powered Attendance Management System:

i.Login Screen – Users can securely log in to access the system.

ii.Face Recognition in Action – The system detects and recognizes faces in real time to mark attendance automatically.

iii.Attendance Dashboard – Shows the recorded attendance with date, time, and recognized students.

iv.Reports – Generate attendance reports for easy tracking and analysis.

These screenshots provide a quick overview of the system’s functionality and demonstrate how the project works in practice.
